{"tid":1403752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係我唔好我做錯了，希望各位原諒，入黎睇睇。","createTime":"2019-08-03T21:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:45:15.000Z","uid":36797,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3858dd50578dca97902a02e9eeeb670af2893d20","tid":1403752,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:56:58.000Z","msg":"我開左個鳩post叫十八區勇武排行榜，我怕而家煽動到大家太high太自信，聽日會出事。<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳唔易打，好易比人block main road封死，我地目的係黑警一次比一次捉得少人，要做到咁係要鬥智鬥團結，輕敵永遠都係連登仔最易犯既錯，好似之前以為自己撚到狗跟手fake左啲手足出去支援個無人既地方，玩到自己人。<br />\n<br />\n跟據往積，我地每仗贏都係贏在有勇有謀，何況今日仲有至少廿個義士被捕，絕對唔叫贏。<br />\n開心一陣可以，懇求各位千萬不要輕敵，更加唔好為左一爭長短亂下決定，一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17d83eeb207a2269e52549778bbf7a920bd1077","tid":1403752,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe418dd6a1af11526989bae6a499b71a0146c24","tid":1403752,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T22:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7f051d1388248dc7aef6fb08eabe85a8c66ca1","tid":1403752,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T22:17:07.000Z","msg":"聽日去前線贖罪啦"},{"pid":"8def762a03e6403566a052125fd52ad038fa2ac8","tid":1403752,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T22:18:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" da